reviews.name: Furinno 99811 Turn-N-Tube 5-Tier Corner Display Rack Multipurpose Shelving Unit
reviews.reviewText: Arrived on time,easy to put together. Decent product for price,does the job and looks great. Yes,can come off as flemsy buy there's an added hook and tie, I didn't use it. Instead I used a candle as weight.
reviews.title: great product for price

reviews.name: Furinno 99811 Turn-N-Tube 5-Tier Corner Display Rack Multipurpose Shelving Unit
reviews.reviewText: This was a great buy. It looks expensive but is not. Every one who visits ask how they can get them. We placed two in,opposite corners with family pictures and it's a real show case. Love them.
reviews.title: Corner Rack
